{"tid":1309384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(極醜惡) 警方重申定義612為暴動","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T06:46:35.000Z","uid":78068,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb4f1f9c6f11103056c95174b2f8e78a5fabf605","tid":1309384,"uid":78068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Giq8Bhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiq8Bhv.jpg&h=c22132ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n政府多次聲明無為612定性暴動，<br />\n但當民線投訴警方喺無暴動情況底下，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>發放150枚催淚彈</strong></span>，<br />\n包括有不反對通知書嘅中信大廈，險釀人踩人，<br />\n今日，警方聲明白紙黑字重申當日已<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">定義暴動</span></ins></strong>，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以佢鍾意掟邊就掟邊！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/p.2351767344870643/2351767344870643/?type=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fp.2351767344870643%2F2351767344870643%2F%3Ftype%3D1&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUypktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=7362f874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/p.2351767344870643/2351767344870643/?type=1</a><br />\n<br />\n推到畀多啲人知，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，</span></strong><br />\n從未答允！！！！！"},{"pid":"e04f1c4e59041afca0f51160f49a8baf52ce8d04","tid":1309384,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6b2d9cd144f0c8c378bb9e2c2367eed29b5f542e","tid":1309384,"uid":9049,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"又講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02e4743fc05a42ecd1306874711359d2b69276","tid":1309384,"uid":167692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201